queries.name: dbdemos HLS - patient summary
queries.query:
SELECT c.concept_name gender, p.day_of_birth, p.month_of_birth, p.year_of_birth, COUNT(person_id) AS num_persons_count
FROM dbdemos.hls_patient_readmission.person p
LEFT JOIN dbdemos.hls_patient_readmission.concept c ON c.concept_id = p.gender_concept_id
WHERE birth_datetime BETWEEN '{{ from }}' AND '{{ to }}'
GROUP BY c.concept_name, p.day_of_birth, p.month_of_birth, p.year_of_birth
ORDER BY p.year_of_birth ASC

queries.name: dbdemos HLS - Total Patients
queries.query:
SELECT COUNT(person_id) AS num_persons_count
FROM dbdemos.hls_patient_readmission.person
WHERE birth_datetime BETWEEN '{{ from }}' AND '{{ to }}'

queries.name: dbdemos HLS - Patients by State
queries.query:
SELECT NVL(state, 'XX' ) state_abbr, 
    count(*) as Num_Persons_count
FROM dbdemos.hls_patient_readmission.person p
LEFT JOIN dbdemos.hls_patient_readmission.location_ref lr ON p.person_id = lr.person_id
WHERE birth_datetime BETWEEN '{{ from }}' AND '{{ to }}'
GROUP BY state_abbr
ORDER BY 1;
